#: ../../source/index.rst:51
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

#: ../../source/index.rst:53
msgid ""
"PREP-SHOT reads CSVs from a scenario directory, builds a linear program "
"with the ``PyOptInterface`` modeling layer, hands it to the solver, and "
"writes the solved variables back as a NetCDF file:"
msgstr ""
"PREP-SHOT 从算例目录读取 CSV,使用 ``PyOptInterface`` 建模层构建线性规划,交由求解器求解,再将求解结果写回 "
"NetCDF 文件:"

#: ../../source/index.rst:69
msgid ""
"Each scenario directory under ``examples/`` is self-contained "
"(``config.json`` + ``params.json`` + ``input/``); the package discovers "
"everything from there. The dashed arrow is the head- iteration loop: "
"PREP-SHOT solves at fixed water heads, recomputes heads from the "
"resulting reservoir trajectory, and re-solves until convergence "
"(controlled by ``iteration_number`` and ``error_threshold`` in "
"``config.json``)."
msgstr ""
"``examples/`` 下的每个算例目录都是自包含的 (``config.json`` + ``params.json`` + "
"``input/``);程序从该目录发现所需的全部资源。虚线箭头表示水头迭代循环:PREP-SHOT "
"在固定水头下求解,然后从新得到的水库轨迹重新计算水头并再次求解,直到收敛 (由 ``config.json`` 中的 "
"``iteration_number`` 与 ``error_threshold`` 控制)。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:78
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "核心特性"

#: ../../source/index.rst:79
msgid ""
"PREP-SHOT is an optimization model based on linear programming for energy"
" systems with multiple zones."
msgstr "PREP-SHOT 是一个基于线性规划的多区域能源系统优化模型。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:80
msgid "It aims to minimize costs while meeting the given demand time series."
msgstr "在满足给定需求时序的前提下,最小化总成本。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:81
msgid ""
"By default, it operates on hourly-spaced time steps, but this can be "
"adjusted."
msgstr "默认按小时步长运行,可根据需要调整。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:82
msgid ""
"The input data is in long-format (\"tidy\") CSV, while output data is "
"generated in a NetCDF format using `Xarray "
"<https://docs.xarray.dev/en/stable/>`_."
msgstr ""
"输入数据采用长格式 (\"整洁\") CSV;输出数据通过 `Xarray "
"<https://docs.xarray.dev/en/stable/>`_ 写入 NetCDF 格式。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:83
msgid ""
"It supports multiple types of solvers such as `HiGHS <https://github.com"
"/jump-dev/HiGHS.jl>`_ , `GUROBI <https://www.gurobi.com/>`_, `COPT "
"<https://www.copt.de/>`_, and `MOSEK <https://www.mosek.com/>`_ via "
"`PyOptInterface <https://github.com/metab0t/PyOptInterface>`_."
msgstr ""
"通过 `PyOptInterface <https://github.com/metab0t/PyOptInterface>`_ "
"支持多种求解器,如 `HiGHS <https://github.com/jump-dev/HiGHS.jl>`_、`GUROBI "
"<https://www.gurobi.com/>`_、`COPT <https://www.copt.de/>`_、`MOSEK "
"<https://www.mosek.com/>`_。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:84
msgid "It allows the input of multiple scenarios for specific parameters."
msgstr "支持对特定参数输入多套情景。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:85
msgid ""
"As a pure Python program, it benefits from the use of `pandas "
"<https://pandas.pydata.org/>`_ and `Xarray "
"<https://docs.xarray.dev/en/stable/>`_, simplifying complex data analysis"
" and promoting extensibility."
msgstr ""
"作为纯 Python 程序,可借助 `pandas <https://pandas.pydata.org/>`_ 与 `Xarray "
"<https://docs.xarray.dev/en/stable/>`_ 简化复杂的数据分析,提升可扩展性。"

